201
00:30:40.853 --> 00:30:41.936
Ujače…

202
00:30:43.478 --> 00:30:45.395
Odakle ti taj novac?

203
00:30:54.770 --> 00:30:56.103
Od trupla tvoje majke.

204
00:30:57.728 --> 00:30:59.061
Prodao sam ga bolnici.

205
00:31:07.103 --> 00:31:08.770
Prodao si moju majku?

206
00:31:11.436 --> 00:31:13.020
Kako to misliš?

207
00:31:15.103 --> 00:31:15.936
Ujače.

208
00:31:18.478 --> 00:31:20.811
To je tvoja majka željela.

209
00:31:22.020 --> 00:31:26.728
Rekao sam joj da je ovo cijena života.
Tek je tada sklopila oči.


210
00:31:28.603 --> 00:31:31.436
Ovaj je novac tvoja majka.

211
00:31:53.228 --> 00:31:55.103
Pusti me, ujače!

212
00:31:55.186 --> 00:31:57.103
Pusti me!

213
00:31:58.645 --> 00:32:00.811
Pusti me na miru!

214
00:32:02.228 --> 00:32:04.145
-Pusti me.
-Moj Bože.


215
00:32:04.228 --> 00:32:05.061
Pusti me!

216
00:32:05.936 --> 00:32:06.936
Ujače, molim te.

217
00:32:11.145 --> 00:32:12.395
Glupane!

218
00:32:13.520 --> 00:32:17.228
Nije li ti majka rekla da ostaneš živ?

219
00:32:18.853 --> 00:32:23.020
Moraš preživjeti
da bi duša tvoje majke ostala na životu.


220
00:32:23.978 --> 00:32:24.978
Jasno?

221
00:32:27.978 --> 00:32:31.228
Ako ne želiš
da njezina smrt bude uzaludna,


222
00:32:31.728 --> 00:32:32.978
idi i preživi.

